 \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}{1 \over n^{2} + x} = {\pi \over 2x^{1/2}\tanh\pars{\pi x^{1/2}}} - {1 \over 2x}\,, \qquad x > 0 
 x \gg 1 \quad\imp\quad \sum_{n = 1}^{\infty}{1 \over n^{2} + x} \sim \color{#ff0000}{\large{\pi \over 2x^{1/2}}} 
